Package: nearjsonrpc
Title: A Lightweight NEAR Protocol JSON-RPC Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Saw", "Simeon", email = "saw.s@ku.th", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Client utilities for interacting with the NEAR Protocol JSON-RPC API. Provides convenience wrappers
  for common RPC methods (query, block, status, transactions, experimental protocol config) and returns tidy
  tibbles where appropriate. Designed for programmatic access and analysis; does not perform wallet/key
  management.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
